WEBVTT

00:40.880 --> 00:42.280
Smells so good!

00:42.360 --> 00:43.920
What are you cooking?

00:44.880 --> 00:46.040
I really want to eat it!

00:58.120 --> 00:59.600
My sister's making braised food again!

00:59.680 --> 01:01.440
-What is it?
-I won't tell you.

01:11.320 --> 01:12.160
Ning.

01:12.240 --> 01:14.200
Tell Mrs. Zhao not to make dinner tonight.

01:14.280 --> 01:16.160
We'll bring them fatty intestine noodles.

01:18.840 --> 01:19.720
Go ahead.

01:31.240 --> 01:32.760
I really want some.

01:32.840 --> 01:34.560
Little foodie, go on.

01:38.200 --> 01:39.960
Mrs. Zhao.

01:40.040 --> 01:43.040
Changyu said you don't need
to cook dinner tonight.

01:43.120 --> 01:46.680
She'll cook you fatty intestine noodles.

03:14.560 --> 03:19.160
ADAPTED FROM THE NOVEL <i>ZHU YU</i>
BY TUAN ZI LAI XI ON JJWXC.NET

03:24.200 --> 03:25.520
Time for dinner!

03:30.600 --> 03:32.600
Mr. Zhao made you a crutch.

03:34.320 --> 03:35.360
Thank you.

03:51.600 --> 03:52.960
No pig tails.

03:53.880 --> 03:56.640
Today we'll eat meat gourds,
tomorrow we'll have braised pig tails.

04:04.280 --> 04:05.680
Forgot the rule taught by Mother?

04:06.200 --> 04:08.400
How impolite. Let the guest eat first.

04:10.840 --> 04:12.600
Sir, you eat first.

04:13.440 --> 04:14.360
Thank you.

04:43.880 --> 04:45.640
You've been eating congee for a few days.

04:45.720 --> 04:47.240
Will one bowl of noodles be enough?

04:48.920 --> 04:50.400
One bowl of noodles

04:51.000 --> 04:53.120
-is enough.
-You're recovering, you should eat more.

04:54.720 --> 04:55.920
Have more.

05:00.560 --> 05:01.400
Thank you.

05:09.080 --> 05:09.920
Tasty?

05:11.840 --> 05:12.880
Yes.

05:14.320 --> 05:16.800
What is this meat gourd?

05:16.880 --> 05:17.800
Fatty intestines.

05:21.880 --> 05:22.880
Pig intestines.

05:22.960 --> 05:25.640
I was afraid
you wouldn't be used to offal.

05:25.720 --> 05:27.760
Seeing you enjoy it puts my mind at ease.

05:27.840 --> 05:28.960
Don't worry.

05:29.040 --> 05:30.800
I washed the feces inside until it was…

05:33.320 --> 05:34.360
I…

05:35.600 --> 05:37.240
I already washed it very clean.

05:37.320 --> 05:40.880
It's just that Mr. Zhao likes the kind
that's only washed once.

05:40.960 --> 05:43.200
He says a bit of funk makes it tastier.

05:46.640 --> 05:47.840
You gave me quite a fright!

05:48.880 --> 05:50.400
What?

05:50.480 --> 05:52.840
Do I need to report to you
when I'm about to sneeze?

05:52.920 --> 05:54.640
-You scared me!
-Well, I can't control it.

05:57.320 --> 05:59.040
Are you done?

05:59.120 --> 06:00.280
There's still so much left.

06:01.800 --> 06:03.320
I haven't recovered my strength yet.

06:03.400 --> 06:04.280
I'm already full.

06:04.360 --> 06:06.520
-Really?
-Yes.

06:07.720 --> 06:10.360
-Don't waste it.
-Don't waste it.

06:12.280 --> 06:13.320
Go ahead. Eat.

06:19.920 --> 06:22.440
You usually eat things like this?

06:23.480 --> 06:24.920
How could we eat it every day?

06:27.120 --> 06:28.520
The Spring Festival is almost here.

06:28.600 --> 06:32.320
Only when other households slaughter pigs
do they give Changyu some offal.

06:33.720 --> 06:36.760
I haven't had fatty intestine noodles
in a long time.

06:39.160 --> 06:40.240
Thanks for the noodles.

06:43.360 --> 06:47.400
Tomorrow we'll eat pig tails
because she is going to slaughter a pig.

06:50.200 --> 06:51.720
-You know how to slaughter pigs?
-No.

06:54.480 --> 06:56.440
I'm a delicate girl.

06:56.520 --> 06:57.640
How could I do that?

06:58.440 --> 06:59.680
She is talking nonsense.

07:01.640 --> 07:02.480
Don't listen to her.

07:17.520 --> 07:19.600
Stay put. And be quiet.

07:29.040 --> 07:30.280
Ning, come here.

07:30.800 --> 07:32.240
We're playing hide and seek.

07:35.640 --> 07:38.000
Open the door!

07:42.640 --> 07:43.840
<i>She's a butcher.</i>

08:15.480 --> 08:16.560
Be a good pig in this life.

08:16.640 --> 08:18.480
Be a good person in the next!

08:26.040 --> 08:27.320
I slaughter pigs to feed you.

08:38.240 --> 08:40.640
Changning, wash your face.

08:45.040 --> 08:45.880
Come.

08:51.480 --> 08:54.440
Changyu, where's your silver hairpin?

08:55.000 --> 08:58.160
-I pawned it.
-You pawned the hairpin Mother gave you?

08:58.240 --> 08:59.600
Mother will be upset.

09:02.520 --> 09:05.320
Don't worry.
I made an agreement with Shopkeeper Luo.

09:06.280 --> 09:08.280
When I earn money,
I'll redeem it immediately.

09:09.000 --> 09:10.000
Is Ms. Fan here?

09:12.120 --> 09:12.960
Ms. Fan.

09:13.760 --> 09:16.080
-Chef Li sent me to pick up half a pig.
-Alright.

09:32.800 --> 09:34.840
-Here's the money for the pork.
-Thanks.

09:35.480 --> 09:36.600
Take care.

09:45.800 --> 09:48.640
Changyu, when did you slaughter the pig?

09:48.720 --> 09:50.200
I did it at the break of dawn.

09:52.400 --> 09:55.080
Stop telling people
your sister is a butcher.

09:55.760 --> 09:57.640
You pawned the hairpin

09:57.720 --> 09:59.800
to support that handsome gentleman?

10:02.200 --> 10:04.880
Lower your voice. Someone might hear.

10:05.760 --> 10:08.280
I'm doing it to help someone.

10:08.800 --> 10:10.000
But Mrs. Zhao is right.

10:10.600 --> 10:12.600
Feeding a man is really expensive.

10:12.680 --> 10:14.640
I need to work even harder to earn money.

10:15.320 --> 10:18.800
SOUTH MARKET

10:18.880 --> 10:20.840
PORK

10:27.280 --> 10:29.520
FAN'S PORK SHOP

10:29.600 --> 10:33.600
FAN'S PORK SHOP

10:51.800 --> 10:54.680
DUMPLING RESTAURANT

11:07.000 --> 11:08.040
You're covered in sweat.

11:11.280 --> 11:12.280
Are you impressed?

11:18.920 --> 11:20.920
Father, Mother, I've brought food.

11:24.200 --> 11:25.280
Look.

11:25.360 --> 11:27.600
You got covered in sweat,
just like your father.

11:28.640 --> 11:30.360
-Let's eat.
-All right.

11:30.440 --> 11:31.280
Let's go.

11:32.840 --> 11:34.080
Here, Father.

11:34.720 --> 11:35.680
Mother.

11:36.240 --> 11:37.120
Ning.

11:37.640 --> 11:39.200
-How is it, Father?
-Delicious.

11:39.720 --> 11:41.240
I love your cooking.

11:43.960 --> 11:45.080
Changyu.

11:45.840 --> 11:49.120
Your family's pork shop
is going to reopen?

11:52.680 --> 11:53.640
Yes.

11:54.840 --> 11:56.040
Just like my parents.

11:57.040 --> 11:57.880
GUO'S PORK STALL, FAN'S PORK STALL

11:57.960 --> 11:59.040
Hello. Welcome!

12:00.600 --> 12:03.000
How about this piece of meat?
This one is fresh.

12:03.520 --> 12:04.360
Fresh?

12:04.440 --> 12:05.280
YAN'S NOODLE RESTAURANT

12:05.360 --> 12:07.240
Fresh. Guaranteed fresh.

12:08.400 --> 12:10.280
How do you sell your offal?

12:10.360 --> 12:11.400
Madam.

12:12.240 --> 12:13.720
Today we don't sell it separately.

12:13.800 --> 12:15.920
Today our shop is newly opened.

12:16.000 --> 12:18.960
Buy a <i>jin</i> of pork, get an extra liang
of offal. First come, first served.

12:19.800 --> 12:21.520
That's such a good deal.

12:22.320 --> 12:23.880
Then give me five <i>jin</i> of pork belly.

12:23.960 --> 12:25.320
All right!

12:25.400 --> 12:27.440
Our pork belly is 20 mace per <i>jin</i>.

12:27.520 --> 12:29.600
You are our first customer today,

12:29.680 --> 12:31.040
so we'll charge you 18.

12:32.080 --> 12:33.560
You've a sharp mind for trade.

12:33.640 --> 12:36.320
I'll buy from you again next time.

12:36.400 --> 12:38.520
Here, take the pork.

12:38.600 --> 12:39.560
All right.

12:41.800 --> 12:43.000
This is the offal for you.

12:43.080 --> 12:45.040
-Come again.
-Thank you.

12:45.840 --> 12:47.000
Here's the money.

12:48.320 --> 12:50.000
-Thank you.
-Come again next time.

12:50.080 --> 12:52.400
-I sure will.
-Good.

12:52.480 --> 12:53.920
How do you sell the meat?

12:54.000 --> 12:55.480
The meat is very fresh.

12:55.560 --> 12:57.040
The belly is 20 mace per <i>jin</i>.

12:57.120 --> 12:58.680
Give me one <i>jin</i>.

12:58.760 --> 13:01.320
Buy a <i>jin</i> of pork,
get an extra liang of offal.

13:02.280 --> 13:03.520
This is for you.

13:03.600 --> 13:05.840
-Hey! Fan Changyu!
-Thank you.

13:05.920 --> 13:08.200
-Changyu, stop selling!
-Mr. Guo.

13:08.720 --> 13:11.600
You can't break the rules
when doing business, right?

13:11.680 --> 13:13.200
You opened your shop, fine.

13:13.280 --> 13:14.800
What do you mean by giving freebies?

13:14.880 --> 13:16.160
Mr. Guo.

13:16.240 --> 13:18.560
I'm giving freebies today
because it's a new opening,

13:18.640 --> 13:20.040
for good luck.

13:20.120 --> 13:21.720
Which rule did I break?

13:21.800 --> 13:24.000
This counts as breaking the rules.

13:24.520 --> 13:27.440
Who sells pork
and gives away offal for free?

13:27.520 --> 13:28.960
Alright, Guo Dali.

13:29.040 --> 13:32.080
Don't argue with a junior.
She's only selling half a pig.

13:32.160 --> 13:35.960
-I'm talking to her, not you
-Right, Mr. Guo.

13:36.040 --> 13:38.120
You think losing my parents

13:38.200 --> 13:40.920
makes me easy to push around?

13:41.520 --> 13:42.600
Exactly!

13:42.680 --> 13:44.040
You can't do that.

13:44.120 --> 13:45.880
-Bullying a young lady.
-It's bullying.

13:45.960 --> 13:47.160
You're too outrageous!

13:48.200 --> 13:50.000
Fine.

13:50.080 --> 13:52.040
Just for today. Do not do so tomorrow.

13:53.400 --> 13:54.520
All right!

13:54.600 --> 13:56.440
I only planned to do so
for one day anyway.

13:57.360 --> 13:59.000
Go ahead.

13:59.080 --> 14:00.800
You're always meddling.

14:01.840 --> 14:03.160
I still have to sell it for money.

14:06.320 --> 14:09.120
Fan's Pork Stall is newly opened!

14:09.200 --> 14:10.600
Buy pork, get braised offal for free!

14:10.680 --> 14:14.000
Twenty mace per <i>jin</i>, especially fresh!

14:14.080 --> 14:15.800
Pork belly, 20 mace per <i>jin</i> today!

14:15.880 --> 14:17.320
-How much do you want?
-One <i>jin</i>.

14:17.400 --> 14:18.640
-One <i>jin</i>.
-Three <i>jin</i>.

14:19.560 --> 14:20.520
Two hundred seventy,

14:21.680 --> 14:22.600
two hundred eighty,

14:23.800 --> 14:25.120
two hundred ninety.

14:25.200 --> 14:27.520
Changyu!

14:28.840 --> 14:31.600
-M. Zhao, today I earned--
-Stop talking.

14:32.440 --> 14:35.680
Your uncle brought those lackeys
from the gambling den.

14:35.760 --> 14:38.320
They're ransacking your house
looking for the title deed.

14:38.400 --> 14:39.280
What?

14:41.600 --> 14:43.000
Scoundrels.

14:43.080 --> 14:46.720
Changyu, why are you carrying a knife?
Don't do anything rash!

14:47.480 --> 14:49.480
Oh no, someone might die.

14:54.640 --> 14:56.840
Song Yan, open the door quickly!

14:56.920 --> 14:57.920
Song Yan.

15:00.120 --> 15:01.280
Song Yan!

15:02.240 --> 15:03.360
Song Yan.

15:03.440 --> 15:05.600
Song Yan, the Fan couple treated you well.

15:05.680 --> 15:07.720
Come out and speak up for Changyu!

15:09.880 --> 15:11.040
Song Yan.

15:12.840 --> 15:15.520
Song Yan, open the door quickly!

15:15.600 --> 15:17.400
I know you're in there.

15:17.480 --> 15:18.640
Song Yan.

15:19.320 --> 15:20.880
Song Yan.

15:20.960 --> 15:22.040
Song Yan.

15:22.120 --> 15:25.000
Saving a life is what matters, Song Yan!

15:25.520 --> 15:26.720
Song Yan.

15:27.320 --> 15:29.960
Sit down and focus on your studies.

15:30.040 --> 15:32.400
-Mother.
-Song Yan, open the door quickly!

15:32.480 --> 15:34.280
Changyu is in trouble. I must go see.

15:34.880 --> 15:37.760
That Fan Daniu is Fan Changyu's uncle.

15:38.480 --> 15:41.760
That's the Fan family's private matter.

15:41.840 --> 15:43.560
What does it have to do with us?

15:43.640 --> 15:46.040
If I can't keep my own house in order,

15:46.120 --> 15:47.680
what business do I have

15:47.760 --> 15:49.560
chasing rank or governing others?

15:50.240 --> 15:51.960
If you walk out that door,

15:52.040 --> 15:55.040
you can forget about
ever sitting the exams.

15:55.760 --> 15:57.040
Song Yan.

15:57.120 --> 15:59.400
All those books you read,
and not a shred of backbone.

16:00.120 --> 16:01.200
Aren't you afraid

16:01.280 --> 16:03.720
your father's spirit
will be shamed in his grave?

16:03.800 --> 16:04.920
Yan,

16:05.760 --> 16:07.800
we went to so much trouble

16:07.880 --> 16:09.720
to break off the engagement
with that jinx.

16:09.800 --> 16:12.520
If you stand up for her today,

16:12.600 --> 16:14.320
wouldn't that give those gossipmongers

16:15.040 --> 16:17.200
chances to tarnish your reputation
for no reason?

16:18.600 --> 16:21.080
Mrs. Zhao, just stop shouting.

16:21.760 --> 16:24.000
Changyu had her engagement broken off.

16:24.080 --> 16:26.880
You tell me, why should the mother
and son care about her?

16:26.960 --> 16:30.160
-Kang. That's enough.
-She lost her parents, so she's pitiful?

16:30.240 --> 16:32.240
Well, my mother died long ago too.

16:32.320 --> 16:33.520
Who pitied me?

16:33.600 --> 16:35.360
There, there.

16:35.440 --> 16:38.280
Song Yan! Song Yan, open the door quickly!

16:38.360 --> 16:40.560
-Mrs. Zhao! Mrs. Zhao!
-Song Yan!

16:41.240 --> 16:42.240
What's wrong with Ning?

16:42.320 --> 16:44.240
She keeps gasping for breath!

16:47.760 --> 16:48.840
Ning!

16:49.920 --> 16:52.440
Ning, don't be afraid.

16:54.720 --> 16:56.480
Come. Don't panic.

16:56.560 --> 16:57.600
Stay calm.

16:59.400 --> 17:00.440
She's here.

17:01.320 --> 17:02.760
She's carrying a knife.

17:02.840 --> 17:04.520
She won't kill a few people, will she?

17:05.040 --> 17:06.920
His brother has barely been laid to rest,

17:07.000 --> 17:08.880
and he's already after his nieces' home.

17:08.960 --> 17:10.000
Even a rabbit bites when cornered.

17:10.599 --> 17:12.560
-Ning.
-Are you alright, Changyu?

17:14.760 --> 17:15.880
Madam Zhuang, Mrs. Zhao.

17:15.960 --> 17:17.720
-Look after her for me.
-I will.

17:26.880 --> 17:28.040
Go, go, go.

17:32.360 --> 17:33.720
Let's see if we can help.

17:47.160 --> 17:48.440
Stop right there!

17:49.680 --> 17:52.560
Changyu, you're here.

17:58.160 --> 18:00.440
MR. JIN

18:00.520 --> 18:01.960
You made it, Ms. Fan.

18:04.280 --> 18:07.440
Take your men and get out of here.

18:09.440 --> 18:11.080
The gambling den operates by the rules.

18:12.360 --> 18:14.160
Fan Daniu says this house is his.

18:15.000 --> 18:16.400
So I came for the title deed

18:19.560 --> 18:20.720
to pay off his debt.

18:21.440 --> 18:23.160
You told him this house is yours?

18:25.960 --> 18:26.800
Changyu.

18:28.560 --> 18:31.040
I was also forced into a corner
with no other way.

18:31.760 --> 18:33.040
My dear niece,

18:33.120 --> 18:34.600
please help your uncle out.

18:35.280 --> 18:37.640
Let me use this house to pay off my debt,

18:37.720 --> 18:38.560
and from now on,

18:39.440 --> 18:41.680
I'll treat you and Ning

18:41.760 --> 18:44.760
as my own daughters, okay?

18:45.840 --> 18:48.400
If you want to pay off a debt,
why not use your own house?

18:49.520 --> 18:53.160
If I use my own house,
where will your aunt and I live?

18:53.240 --> 18:55.800
You and Ning
will get married in the future.

18:55.880 --> 18:57.720
Keeping this house won't be of much use.

18:59.960 --> 19:02.160
What my parents left for me and Ning,

19:02.680 --> 19:04.120
how I handle it is my business.

19:04.200 --> 19:06.720
Hear that? This house isn't his.

19:07.880 --> 19:10.440
I'm your own uncle!

19:10.960 --> 19:12.320
Come here. Come here!

19:13.040 --> 19:14.600
-Mr. Jin! Mr. Jin!
-Don't move!

19:14.680 --> 19:16.120
Mr. Jin!

19:16.200 --> 19:18.040
If the title deed isn't handed over today,

19:19.640 --> 19:22.280
then I'll have no choice
but to chop off one of his hands.

19:23.560 --> 19:25.040
I'll only give you three seconds.

19:26.760 --> 19:27.800
One.

19:28.600 --> 19:29.920
Two.

19:34.360 --> 19:35.680
Use this cleaver.

19:35.760 --> 19:36.600
HAVE A FULL MEAL

19:36.680 --> 19:37.560
The blade is sharp.

19:37.640 --> 19:38.880
One chop down,

19:39.800 --> 19:41.000
everything will be severed.

19:42.200 --> 19:44.400
It will also make my uncle suffer less.

19:46.680 --> 19:48.600
You… You…

19:49.920 --> 19:51.000
You're joking, right?

19:51.080 --> 19:52.960
You started the joke.

20:00.400 --> 20:01.880
Fan Changyu!

20:01.960 --> 20:03.880
You brought death
to your father and mother.

20:03.960 --> 20:06.280
Are you going to bring death to me too?

20:06.800 --> 20:09.440
You, a broken-off engagement,
unwanted brat,

20:09.520 --> 20:12.280
and you still want to seize this property
for your dowry?

20:12.360 --> 20:13.840
Why don't you see who the hell

20:13.920 --> 20:15.280
dares to marry you, jinx?

20:17.960 --> 20:19.040
You.

20:20.960 --> 20:22.440
Get back to your house.

20:22.520 --> 20:24.480
Otherwise, they'll take one of your hands,

20:24.560 --> 20:26.080
and I'll take your life!

20:26.160 --> 20:27.280
I'll kill you first,

20:28.120 --> 20:29.880
then go down and apologize to my parents!

20:29.960 --> 20:30.800
Miss.

20:31.960 --> 20:33.640
Our gambling den also follows reason.

20:34.400 --> 20:35.640
According to the Dayin Code,

20:36.160 --> 20:38.120
no male heir means
it passes to the nearest kin.

20:38.760 --> 20:40.880
If one brother dies, the other inherits.

20:41.400 --> 20:43.120
Even if you go to the court,

20:43.640 --> 20:45.280
this house will still go to Fan Daniu.

20:47.400 --> 20:48.440
That's right.

20:48.520 --> 20:52.040
Gambling den people are so reasonable.

20:52.640 --> 20:54.840
Since the Dayin Code says it's mine,

20:54.920 --> 20:56.080
why are you still standing here?

20:56.720 --> 20:58.000
Give me…

20:59.760 --> 21:01.640
Mr. Jin, let's keep searching.

21:06.800 --> 21:08.280
Search carefully.

21:38.080 --> 21:42.440
SPIRIT TABLET OF MENG LIHUA
SPIRIT TABLET OF FAN ERNIU

21:49.600 --> 21:50.560
Father.

21:51.360 --> 21:53.360
If I disobey and break your commandment,

21:55.440 --> 21:56.600
please don't be angry.

21:58.840 --> 21:59.920
Ning.

22:00.840 --> 22:01.840
Turn around and count to ten.

22:08.920 --> 22:10.160
One.

22:17.960 --> 22:19.000
Two.

22:25.000 --> 22:25.760
Three.

22:29.520 --> 22:30.680
Four.

22:37.960 --> 22:39.160
Five.

22:50.680 --> 22:51.960
Six.

23:00.040 --> 23:01.360
Seven.

23:05.120 --> 23:07.800
-Leave now, or else.
-Eight.

23:08.680 --> 23:10.000
Fools, attack together!

23:13.160 --> 23:14.000
Nine.

23:32.360 --> 23:34.280
I only have to count to nine.

23:35.960 --> 23:38.640
If a girl chases me off,

23:39.280 --> 23:41.320
I'll lose face in this line of work!

23:43.520 --> 23:44.440
Watch out!

24:01.920 --> 24:05.520
Bullying an orphan girl in broad daylight!

24:05.600 --> 24:07.320
Do you still have any…

24:28.480 --> 24:29.400
Constable.

24:32.760 --> 24:34.760
The broken items are all recorded here.

24:35.480 --> 24:38.000
Compensate for these,
and today's matter will be settled.

24:43.280 --> 24:44.280
Jin Yuanbao.

24:44.360 --> 24:46.840
You're already 27 this year,
aren't you, kid?

24:47.800 --> 24:49.600
Not settling down to build a career,

24:49.680 --> 24:51.320
causing trouble all day long.

24:51.400 --> 24:52.840
What would your grandmother say?

24:54.240 --> 24:56.520
After we compensate for her losses,

24:56.600 --> 24:58.400
who will compensate for our medicine?

24:58.480 --> 25:00.800
Four grown men can't even handle one girl?

25:00.880 --> 25:02.240
-I--
-No medicine money.

25:02.320 --> 25:03.680
-I…
-Get lost, now.

25:04.840 --> 25:05.880
Wait!

25:08.440 --> 25:11.480
SPIRIT TABLET OF MENG LIHUA
SPIRIT TABLET OF FAN ERNIU

25:12.200 --> 25:14.720
You knocked over
my parents' memorial tablets earlier.

25:16.840 --> 25:18.640
You must apologize before you can leave.

25:19.640 --> 25:20.720
Constable.

25:20.800 --> 25:23.240
This house should belong to me.

25:23.320 --> 25:27.240
If you want to claim the house, put it
in writing and submit it to the court.

25:27.320 --> 25:28.320
I…

25:28.400 --> 25:31.000
But damaging the memorial tablet,
if it goes to the court,

25:31.080 --> 25:31.920
it's 20 strokes.

25:38.200 --> 25:40.000
Mr. Fan, Mrs. Fan.

25:40.080 --> 25:41.800
-We're sorry.
-We're sorry.

25:41.880 --> 25:43.960
You are magnanimous. We were wrong.

25:44.040 --> 25:46.560
-We're sorry.
-We're sorry.

25:53.600 --> 25:54.560
The money.

25:59.960 --> 26:00.800
You may leave.

26:05.960 --> 26:07.480
-Let's go.
-Can I have a word?

26:08.200 --> 26:09.880
-Go.
-Mr. Jin. Mr. Jin.

26:09.960 --> 26:11.040
Mr. Jin.

26:16.480 --> 26:17.320
Keep it for Changyu.

26:17.400 --> 26:19.000
I knew it.

26:19.080 --> 26:20.760
Asking for your help was right.

26:21.600 --> 26:23.400
Although Fan Erniu has passed,

26:23.480 --> 26:25.200
your friendship remains.

26:25.280 --> 26:26.920
But regarding the house matter,

26:27.440 --> 26:28.680
I'm afraid it's not over.

26:31.320 --> 26:32.200
Changyu.

26:35.920 --> 26:36.760
Changyu.

26:39.160 --> 26:42.040
Forcing a young lady
to hold up this household.

26:43.120 --> 26:44.640
What a sin.

26:48.040 --> 26:49.080
Father.

26:50.000 --> 26:52.000
The long-handled saber technique
you taught me,

26:52.680 --> 26:56.320
which I must not reveal
in front of outsiders…

26:57.800 --> 26:59.280
I didn't obey today.

27:00.280 --> 27:02.640
I beg Father and Mother not to blame me.

27:05.720 --> 27:07.200
Your father surely won't blame you.

27:11.320 --> 27:12.760
With injuries like that,

27:12.840 --> 27:14.080
you should be resting.

27:14.160 --> 27:15.360
What are you doing out here?

27:16.120 --> 27:17.200
It was too noisy earlier.

27:17.720 --> 27:18.720
I couldn't sit still.

27:28.680 --> 27:29.840
Fan Erniu.

27:32.720 --> 27:34.440
Your father can not only slaughter pigs,

27:35.920 --> 27:37.000
but also do saber techniques.

27:39.040 --> 27:40.400
You heard everything.

27:44.240 --> 27:45.920
Before he became a butcher,

27:46.440 --> 27:47.600
my father was a convoy guard.

27:49.240 --> 27:51.120
Your mother's name is Meng Lihua.

27:52.760 --> 27:53.800
Is that her real name?

27:56.320 --> 27:57.720
My mother was amazing.

27:59.200 --> 28:00.680
She could read and write,

28:02.360 --> 28:03.880
blend fragrances, and make powders.

28:04.880 --> 28:06.280
Other butchers,

28:06.360 --> 28:07.800
when they slaughter a pig at home,

28:08.520 --> 28:09.960
they're covered in the smell.

28:10.480 --> 28:11.720
But my home wasn't like that.

28:12.480 --> 28:14.280
After the clothes were washed,

28:14.360 --> 28:16.680
they were fumigated
with the fragrance Mother blended.

28:18.360 --> 28:19.800
Not a trace of odor remained.

28:20.320 --> 28:21.760
Fellows, nothing more here.

28:21.840 --> 28:22.880
Stop looking.

28:22.960 --> 28:25.160
Disperse. Go back.

28:26.520 --> 28:27.480
Thank you.

28:27.560 --> 28:29.720
Today, they were clearly wrong.

28:31.960 --> 28:33.320
But what they said is right.

28:33.400 --> 28:35.520
If Fan Daniu really submits a petition,

28:36.280 --> 28:37.920
Changyu probably can't keep this house.

28:38.000 --> 28:39.480
Then what should they do?

28:40.000 --> 28:42.320
These two girls are now
alone and helpless.

28:42.400 --> 28:44.200
You absolutely must help with this.

28:44.280 --> 28:46.000
I never said I wouldn't help.

28:51.680 --> 28:53.520
It's not without a solution.

28:56.040 --> 28:58.560
How did your parents pass away?

28:59.480 --> 29:00.440
Mountain bandits.

29:01.240 --> 29:02.680
Father had his throat slit.

29:03.560 --> 29:04.680
He died on the spot.

29:05.200 --> 29:08.200
When Mother was brought back,
she still had a breath left.

29:11.200 --> 29:13.160
She struggled for three or four hours,

29:15.320 --> 29:17.640
just to say a word to me and Ning.

29:21.200 --> 29:23.680
But in the end,
she couldn't utter half a sentence.

29:29.120 --> 29:31.040
She just handed me
the hairpin in her hand.

29:34.880 --> 29:36.720
I'm sure they won't blame you.

29:41.160 --> 29:44.080
This gauze hasn't been stained with blood.
It's clean.

29:47.520 --> 29:48.560
Thanks.

29:49.320 --> 29:50.440
Compared to me,

29:50.960 --> 29:52.680
your parents at least accompanied you.

29:55.640 --> 29:57.480
At least you still have
your younger sister,

29:57.560 --> 29:58.720
a close blood relative.

30:00.320 --> 30:01.440
At least,

30:01.520 --> 30:03.280
you have a home you've lived in for years.

30:04.360 --> 30:05.800
But since childhood,

30:07.120 --> 30:08.680
my parents have already been gone.

30:11.560 --> 30:13.440
How did your parents die?

30:22.800 --> 30:23.840
They died in the war.

30:32.280 --> 30:35.400
Then we're both without parents.

30:36.840 --> 30:38.560
Look at us, comparing who's had it worse.

30:40.320 --> 30:43.400
Sorry for making you recall sad things.

30:46.680 --> 30:48.120
Now you know,

30:49.560 --> 30:52.080
I'm just a pig-slaughtering woman
with brute strength.

30:52.600 --> 30:53.760
Laugh if you want.

30:57.760 --> 30:59.280
You not only saved me,

31:00.200 --> 31:01.360
but also raised money,

31:01.880 --> 31:02.960
wanting to feed me.

31:03.680 --> 31:06.400
If I laugh again, wouldn't that
make me an ungrateful snake?

31:11.520 --> 31:14.640
Changyu. Changyu.

31:14.720 --> 31:16.560
Mrs. Zhao is asking for you.

31:17.240 --> 31:18.320
Don't tell them I cried.

31:20.640 --> 31:21.680
Let's go.

31:22.240 --> 31:23.280
Be careful.

31:25.920 --> 31:27.440
Is his body okay?

31:27.520 --> 31:28.640
Can he recover later?

31:28.720 --> 31:32.120
At most, there might be some
lasting issues with his legs and feet.

31:32.200 --> 31:34.040
-It won't affect anything else.
-Mr. and Mrs. Zhao.

31:34.800 --> 31:36.000
You're here, Changyu.

31:36.600 --> 31:37.560
Come here.

31:38.760 --> 31:41.000
We have something to discuss with you.

31:43.240 --> 31:45.880
-You've got snow in your hair.
-What's the matter?

31:46.400 --> 31:47.400
So mysterious.

31:58.760 --> 31:59.600
‎You tell her.

32:04.880 --> 32:06.920
Mrs. Zhao, tell me.

32:07.000 --> 32:08.320
I'll definitely do as you say.

32:14.560 --> 32:15.720
A live-in husband?

32:18.520 --> 32:21.480
This was Constable Wang's idea.
You can trust it.

32:21.560 --> 32:25.080
You see, this way
your father will have an heir,

32:25.160 --> 32:26.680
and the house will stay in your name.

32:26.760 --> 32:28.200
Fan Daniu can not take it anymore.

32:28.800 --> 32:31.960
Your parents only left this house
for you sisters.

32:32.040 --> 32:35.400
If you lose this too, how will you live?

32:35.480 --> 32:38.120
Exactly.
What girl marries without her parents

32:38.200 --> 32:40.560
carefully choosing the match for her?

32:41.320 --> 32:42.680
Changyu really has a hard life.

32:42.760 --> 32:45.240
What good young man
would take a live-in marriage?

32:45.320 --> 32:46.640
She has been forced to do so.

32:46.720 --> 32:50.240
If she wants to keep the house,
she must take in a live-in husband.

32:50.320 --> 32:51.680
What does it mean to take in a husband?

32:52.280 --> 32:53.880
It means in the future,

32:53.960 --> 32:56.520
find a man for your sister
who can live with her for a lifetime

32:56.600 --> 32:58.160
and take good care of you.

32:59.600 --> 33:02.560
-Then I want that handsome gentleman.
-No.

33:03.320 --> 33:04.240
Why not?

33:04.880 --> 33:07.160
Based on my years of experience
as a matchmaker,

33:07.760 --> 33:09.360
he's a good young man.

33:10.360 --> 33:12.160
Mrs. Zhao, you just said it yourself.

33:12.240 --> 33:14.440
What good young man
would take a live-in marriage?

33:14.520 --> 33:16.880
She has been a matchmaker
for over ten years.

33:16.960 --> 33:18.920
She's seen more young men
than you've seen pigs.

33:19.000 --> 33:21.400
You have to listen to the expert
on this matter.

33:21.960 --> 33:24.760
Also, the war in Chongzhou is intense.

33:24.840 --> 33:26.240
I heard they're recruiting again.

33:26.320 --> 33:29.080
Now every household
is making arrangements for marriages,

33:29.160 --> 33:30.880
just to leave an heir for the family.

33:30.960 --> 33:32.040
Finding a live-in husband

33:32.120 --> 33:34.080
is harder than reaching the sky!

33:34.160 --> 33:35.600
-Anyway, he won't do.
-Why?

33:35.680 --> 33:37.720
-He just won't do!
-What's wrong with him?

33:37.800 --> 33:40.080
-He…
-Alright, alright, keep it down.

33:41.400 --> 33:42.640
Well, Yan Zheng,

33:43.160 --> 33:45.120
although he's quite badly injured,

33:45.720 --> 33:48.320
after recovering, his legs and feet
might have lasting issues,

33:48.400 --> 33:50.600
and he doesn't have
any identity or travel documents.

33:50.680 --> 33:52.000
However,

33:52.720 --> 33:53.560
the advantage is

33:54.280 --> 33:55.960
he's readily available.

33:56.040 --> 33:57.040
Right?

33:57.120 --> 33:59.560
Changyu,
this settles both your problems at once.

33:59.640 --> 34:00.960
You'd be helping each other.

34:01.040 --> 34:02.520
It doesn't count as leveraging.

34:02.600 --> 34:03.640
-But--
-Exactly so.

34:04.200 --> 34:06.440
You just said
you'd definitely do as I say.

34:06.520 --> 34:08.800
-Mrs. Zhao.
-What?

34:08.880 --> 34:09.920
Mr. Zhao.

34:10.520 --> 34:13.719
I know you two are doing this
for me and Changning's sake.

34:14.239 --> 34:16.840
But I need time to think about it.

34:17.760 --> 34:19.600
What's there to think about?

34:19.679 --> 34:21.080
-Changyu.
-Changyu.

34:21.159 --> 34:22.120
Changyu.

34:29.239 --> 34:30.320
Why are you sighing?

34:40.320 --> 34:41.480
Changyu.

34:42.080 --> 34:43.760
Talk to me.

34:43.840 --> 34:45.360
What's wrong with that lad?

34:50.199 --> 34:51.239
Is he…

34:51.320 --> 34:52.679
not exactly fit for the job?

34:54.480 --> 34:57.400
It's okay. I'll ask Mr. Zhao
to see if it can still be treated.

34:57.480 --> 34:59.440
That's not what I meant.

34:59.520 --> 35:01.160
Don't speculate about it.

35:01.920 --> 35:04.160
What if he's unwilling?

35:05.560 --> 35:07.880
Changyu, you're pretty as a peach

35:07.960 --> 35:09.480
and can butcher hogs to feed a household.

35:09.560 --> 35:10.960
He dares turn you down?

35:11.480 --> 35:13.640
Besides, he doesn't even have
identity or travel documents.

35:13.720 --> 35:14.800
Once married,

35:14.880 --> 35:17.800
at least he won't be treated as a refugee
and forced into the vanguard.

35:17.880 --> 35:19.560
I only just saved him,

35:20.280 --> 35:21.680
and now I'd make him marry in?

35:22.520 --> 35:23.800
This is holding past kindness over him.

35:26.320 --> 35:28.280
Never mind whether he's willing.

35:29.240 --> 35:30.640
Given enough time,

35:32.840 --> 35:34.680
he might turn into another Song Yan.

35:38.280 --> 35:41.040
Since ancient times,
unfaithful men are often scholars.

35:41.560 --> 35:43.520
He's not a scholar.

35:44.160 --> 35:46.280
He's not like that ungrateful Song Yan.

35:50.840 --> 35:51.720
Mrs. Zhao.

35:53.040 --> 35:54.400
Yan Zheng

35:55.640 --> 35:57.240
is like a piece of high-quality jade

35:57.320 --> 35:59.480
I found in the snow.

36:00.400 --> 36:01.240
Beautiful,

36:02.040 --> 36:02.960
smooth,

36:03.480 --> 36:04.560
and valuable.

36:05.320 --> 36:06.680
But it's not mine.

36:07.640 --> 36:10.640
Even if I carve Fan Changyu on it,
he is not mine.

36:11.240 --> 36:13.080
Then carve your name on it and keep it.

36:13.600 --> 36:16.320
When someone comes, it's not like
we said we wouldn't return it.

36:18.560 --> 36:20.040
He also said

36:21.000 --> 36:22.880
once he's recovered, he will leave.

36:24.080 --> 36:26.600
Once he has a virtuous
and capable wife like you

36:26.680 --> 36:28.480
and lives a stable life,
how could he leave?

36:29.080 --> 36:31.160
Maybe even if you drive him away,
he won't leave.

36:32.000 --> 36:33.480
My dear, dear Mrs. Zhao.

36:33.560 --> 36:35.920
Forcing him to marry
into the family of a butcher…

36:37.160 --> 36:38.960
A melon forced off the vine is not sweet.

36:39.040 --> 36:40.960
It doesn't need to be sweet.
Quench the thirst first.

36:41.960 --> 36:43.160
If he dares to say no,

36:43.240 --> 36:44.760
I'll throw him out.

36:44.840 --> 36:47.480
Even a saved donkey
can still turn the millstone.

36:47.560 --> 36:49.280
-If you don't tell him, I'll go.
-Don't!

36:54.600 --> 36:56.200
I'll go tell him myself.

37:15.400 --> 37:16.800
What's the matter?

37:18.280 --> 37:19.280
Come in.

37:31.360 --> 37:32.280
I…

37:33.680 --> 37:35.160
I want…

37:40.000 --> 37:41.280
I want to wash your clothes.

37:41.920 --> 37:44.000
-They're clean…
-No need to be polite.

37:48.080 --> 37:49.480
…set of clothes.

37:58.240 --> 38:00.200
Where did the clothes come from?

38:00.280 --> 38:01.400
I stole them.

38:02.400 --> 38:03.760
I'm going to wash clothes.

38:04.880 --> 38:06.240
I'll help you.

38:27.160 --> 38:28.160
Here.

38:37.600 --> 38:38.960
Yan Zheng.

38:41.760 --> 38:43.240
Will you marry into my family?

38:44.320 --> 38:45.480
Is that okay?

38:47.320 --> 38:50.320
When my injuries heal and I leave,
I will naturally give you money.

38:53.000 --> 38:55.000
I don't want money. I want you.

38:55.800 --> 38:57.480
If you say no, see if I don't beat you up.

39:01.360 --> 39:02.600
If I don't beat you to death,

39:03.120 --> 39:04.920
you'll have to pay even more for medicine.

39:06.240 --> 39:07.480
You…

39:08.040 --> 39:09.600
Stop yelping.

39:10.120 --> 39:10.960
This is serious.

39:12.160 --> 39:14.440
You are now playing the role of Yan Zheng.

39:14.520 --> 39:15.440
Be serious.

39:20.320 --> 39:22.480
Yesterday, the man failed
to seize the title deed.

39:23.680 --> 39:24.680
Next,

39:26.600 --> 39:28.360
he will submit a petition
to the authorities.

39:29.760 --> 39:31.400
If I want to keep this house,

39:32.320 --> 39:33.680
the only way

39:35.240 --> 39:36.880
is to take in a live-in husband.

39:41.320 --> 39:42.600
Father and Mother are dead.

39:46.160 --> 39:47.840
Only this house is left.

39:49.680 --> 39:51.280
Even if it's for Ning's sake,

39:54.000 --> 39:55.640
I can't lose this home.

39:59.160 --> 40:01.560
I'm not necessarily forcing you
to marry into my family.

40:02.160 --> 40:03.480
I'm just…

40:06.440 --> 40:07.520
here to ask.

40:20.680 --> 40:23.160
The air is dry.

40:23.960 --> 40:26.920
Beware of fire.

40:27.600 --> 40:28.480
Come in.

40:34.240 --> 40:36.040
Mr. and Mrs. Zhao are already asleep.

40:36.120 --> 40:37.520
I was worried
no one was looking after you.

40:42.160 --> 40:43.520
Blood loss has left you chilled.

40:43.600 --> 40:45.440
This tea water is cold.
Better not drink it.

40:46.000 --> 40:47.160
I made some soup for you.

40:48.120 --> 40:49.240
Thank you.

41:00.320 --> 41:01.320
This is…

41:02.040 --> 41:03.240
Pig liver soup. It nourishes the blood.

41:07.760 --> 41:10.560
There was still some offal left
from yesterday's sales,

41:10.640 --> 41:11.880
so I cooked this for you.

41:18.360 --> 41:19.320
It's a bit hot.

41:19.840 --> 41:20.680
I'll drink it later.

41:25.680 --> 41:27.320
You don't like pig offal, right?

41:29.680 --> 41:31.760
Yesterday's fatty intestine noodles too,

41:31.840 --> 41:33.080
you only ate a few bites.

41:33.920 --> 41:34.880
The pig liver soup too.

41:41.280 --> 41:42.720
I wouldn't say I dislike it.

41:43.440 --> 41:44.840
It's just that I'm somewhat…

41:45.760 --> 41:46.600
not used to it.

41:50.160 --> 41:51.320
But…

41:52.320 --> 41:54.240
This is best I can provide.

41:56.080 --> 41:58.720
This can nourish your blood.
It's good for you.

42:00.000 --> 42:03.160
Just drink it as if it were medicine.

42:07.240 --> 42:08.080
I'll go now.

42:12.200 --> 42:13.040
Ms. Fan.

42:23.400 --> 42:24.240
I agree.

42:26.280 --> 42:27.400
Then drink it while it's warm.

42:28.440 --> 42:29.640
What I mean is…

42:31.200 --> 42:32.440
about marrying into your family.

42:33.120 --> 42:34.240
I agree.

42:55.960 --> 42:57.000
Good.

43:02.680 --> 43:04.000
If you stay,

43:06.360 --> 43:07.360
I'll slaughter pigs to feed you.

45:59.440 --> 46:02.760
NO ANIMALS WERE HARMED
IN THE MAKING OF THIS EPISODE

46:02.840 --> 46:03.760
Subtitle translation by: Peng Peng
